Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:23.46,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(298,0)}We sigh whenever we're about to come to a standstill
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:29.71,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}While moving on this endless journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:37.43,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Everytime we lunge for it, it escapes and flies off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:44.85,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}But now, there's nothing to be afraid of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:52.78,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}The powerful ties that bind our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:58.24,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Will never come loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:07.96,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9}After a lifetime of searching, we finally arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:13.76,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Here, where the period lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:23.06,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}Let's change all our sorrow and rage to power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:27.98,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,298}Destiny is right within our reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:23.46,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(298,0)}終わりなき旅の途中　立ち止まりそうな時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:29.71,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}深いため息こぼす　僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:37.43,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}掴みかけてはまた離れていった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:44.85,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}でも今はもう何も恐れることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:52.78,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}心を繋ぐ強い絆は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:58.24,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}けして解けはしないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:07.96,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9}探し続けて辿り着いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:13.76,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}この場所で {\fsp8}Perio{\fsp3.2}d に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:23.06,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}悲しみ怒り 力に変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:27.98,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,298}運命はすぐそばに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:23.46,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(298,0)}Owarinaki tabi no tochuu tachidomarisouna toki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:29.71,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Fukai tameiki kobosu bokura wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:37.43,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Tsukamikaketewa mata hanareteitta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:44.85,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Demo ima wa mou nanimo osoreru koto wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:52.78,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}Kokoro wo tsunagu tsuyoi kizuna wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:58.24,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Keshite hodoke wa shinai sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:07.96,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9}Sagashitsuzukete tadoritsuita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:13.76,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Kono basho de piriodo ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:23.06,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}Kanashimi ikari chikara ni kaete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:27.98,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,298}Unmei wa sugu soba ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:19.27,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}The promise we never made
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.06,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:24.90,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}tries to snatch our future away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:30.49,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that we can't rejoice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:31.49,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}straight from the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:36.45,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}when we obtain something we've always been after?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:42.17,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,498}The overflowing tears aren't from feebleness or remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:46.96,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,258)}They're fragments born from agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:52.01,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Of all the moments and destinies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:23:00.77,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I realized there's one absolute certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:03.31,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if things get tough and I'm at my limit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.31,0:23:07.32,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:12.20,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:20.04,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can feel the warmth of your right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:23.71,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}where it's tightly joined with my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:19.27,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}交わしたはずのない約束が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.06,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}今日も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:24.90,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}僕らの未来を奪おうとする
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:30.49,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,欲しがっていたものを手にしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:31.49,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}素直に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:36.45,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}うまく笑えないのはなぜだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:42.17,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,498}あふれる涙は　弱さや後悔じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:46.96,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,258)}イタミが生んだカケラで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:52.01,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}どんな瞬間だって運命だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:23:00.77,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}ひとつだけ確かなものがあると知った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:03.31,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,限界だって困難だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.31,0:23:07.32,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,あきらめたくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:12.20,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,このまま離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:20.04,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}かたく握りしめた　君の右手のぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:23.71,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}ここにあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:19.27,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kawashita hazu no nai yakasoku ga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.06,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kyou mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.06,0:22:24.90,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Bokura no mirai wo ubaou to suru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:30.49,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshigatteita mono wo te ni shitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.49,0:22:31.49,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Sunao ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:36.45,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Umaku waraenai nowa nazedarou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:42.17,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,498}Afureru namida wo yowasa ya koukai ja nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:46.96,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,258)}Itami ga unda kakera de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:52.01,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Donna shunkan datte unmei datte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:23:00.77,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Hitotsu dake tashika na mono ga aru to shitta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:03.31,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Genkai datte konnan datte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.31,0:23:07.32,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Akirametakunaiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:12.20,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomama hanasanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:20.04,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kataku nigirishimeta kimi no migite no nukumori
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.04,0:23:23.71,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Koko ni arukara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.33,0:01:52.13,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,It's that expression again, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:55.30,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that also represents gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:56.72,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.64,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,We're checking to see whether there's a hidden message here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.22,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,A hidden message?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:11.56,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemists often hide their research using trope and hidden meanings to prevent ordinary people from deciphering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:15.32,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,But at a glance, these documents aren't encrypted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.32,0:02:23.33,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,So we're going to note that phrases with "immortality" and "gold" appear quite often to try to view things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.62,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Think you're on to something then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:27.08,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:31.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:32.13,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:32.88,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.17,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:37.59,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried you'd never wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for worrying all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:45.01,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,So, why am I in pieces?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:48.64,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,And that's where we're at now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:53.02,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You were too large to carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.02,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,That is why we had to take you apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:59.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to give you guys so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.91,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Has this ever happened before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:05.16,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Just once, while I was on my way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:11.87,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,It must be inconvenient for you to be scattered in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:14.17,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put you back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.63,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Could you hold on to this for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.26,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.35,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:27.56,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's his right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:31.56,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you're right. We have to put him back together properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.31,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Scattered in pieces...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.03,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Putting things together...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.25,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, May?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.42,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Look at what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.96,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,They're all scattered now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.88,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:09.18,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,...how it would look if we changed the pages' order by grouping terms such as "gold" and "immortality".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.85,0:04:19.69,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,"Golden Being"... I saw that term over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.86,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,"Immortality"... overlaps with these right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.61,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,"Perfect Being"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:26.95,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.49,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Hand me those pages, Marcoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.50,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that ties into these!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.00,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone have a "Golden Being"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.71,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I do. It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.55,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,That should be the last of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.84,0:04:48.72,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:57.81,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.44,0:05:03.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The Nationwide Transmutation Circle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:08.03,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we find out about this now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.70,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.33,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean these research documents won't be of any use at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:14.45,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.45,0:05:15.29,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:15.96,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.58,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to this country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.00,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:26.84,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I was foolish to hope someone else's studies would overturn this crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:34.52,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, is this what you wanted to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:40.40,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, shouldn't you have gotten further than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.65,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,There's still something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:48.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't even realize to take it apart at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:52.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be strange if there was more hidden in these documents!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:55.83,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:06.72,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! What were you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:09.01,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,It's Mother Nature's fault for making it so cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:11.30,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I'm sensitive to the cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.10,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:16.68,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Now we don't know front from back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:22.40,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all these you flipped over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That may be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:27.36,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We need to "overturn" this crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:31.66,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Flip each one of them over from how they were originally!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:41.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:43.92,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:52.43,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,This is a new Amestrian Nationwide Transmutation Circle that is activated when Eastern Alchemy is made a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.66,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any signs of them going this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:15.87,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I took a wrong turn somewhere. I guess I'll go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.20,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:59.83,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,So this place is used to remove the rubble from the tunnel Sloth is digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.50,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Crimson Alchemist, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.63,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Pleasure to meet you. I'm Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:13.72,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.97,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,What happened with Scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:19.18,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:20.72,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Save that for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:24.73,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,First, carve a bloody crest into Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:30.86,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,With all due respect, the soldiers at Briggs are quite monolithic and powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:33.65,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.45,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,You need to utilize that exact strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.92,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,The tunnel being dug by Sloth is almost complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:48.63,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.67,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,As you say, I'll carve a bloody crest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.47,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,To the Briggs fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.65,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.52,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Any changes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.40,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:17.74,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Moving right on, I heard Kimblee has gone missing. Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.07,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.66,0:09:22.54,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,There was an explosion large enough to cause a shaft to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:25.46,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee and a few others are missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:29.38,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,We searched the rubble, but in the end, found no bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.30,Default,Bucca,0000,0000,0000,,Are the "few others" soldiers from Briggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:37.68,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:39.64,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,Two of Kimblee's men...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:43.01,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,...and the Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:51.31,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. The Fullmetal boss, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:53.57,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,I hope he's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.57,0:09:54.53,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,As do I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.15,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,How are things in the west?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:02.58,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting nasty on the Pendleton border.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:07.12,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,From their way of fighting, I can't help but think they're {\i1}trying{\i0\fscx30} {\r} to produce more deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:14.59,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,As you said, it seems like the army is taking the initiative in causing bloodshed to create a transmutation circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.59,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Have you gotten word from\NMaster Sergeant Fuery in the south?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:22.10,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,He called me a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:26.81,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,He says they're having an all-out war with the Aerugon army in South Fotsett.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.70,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,R... Run, Thomas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.79,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,No time to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:47.62,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Thoma-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.63,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.96,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,I will survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.88,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,God dammit, I {\i1}will{\i0\fscx30} {\r} survive!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.39,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:11.27,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we, members of Mustang's old team, aren't so popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:14.27,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been in contact with the Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:19.03,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, in full detail. We've been using a messenger who's acquainted with the Armstrong family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.41,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:24.91,Default,Breda,0000,0000,0000,,Things seem to be getting pretty serious up north, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:27.99,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Serious sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:35.04,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,The underlings of the man who's planning to turn this country into Hell are proceeding steadily with their plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.75,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,but there's not a single thing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.39,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,It's connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:59.28,Default,Sloth,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to work anymore... right... Pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.49,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,The time is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:09.99,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,The day is right within our reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.60,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:33.14,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch is served! Please line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:41.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rose, I'd like to have meat pie next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.45,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make some if we get the ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:53.29,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I don't work here, but do you think you could possibly give these two something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.67,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.04,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,There's plenty for you, too, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This looks so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.18,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Can I get an extra scoop, Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:09.30,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, everyone gets the same amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:12.18,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:16.56,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can I have some, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:24.40,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:26.74,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much. It was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:33.58,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That's a difficult question to answer,\Nsince I've been wandering all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.08,0:13:37.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But why Lior of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:41.25,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of the riot that happened here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:46.38,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing left in this town because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.43,0:13:51.51,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,There are delicious meals here, are there not?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.35,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flattered by your compliment,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:01.77,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,but this is about all I can do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.40,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:09.57,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Both the warm meals you serve and the bright smile on your face motivate everyone to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:15.79,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:21.71,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I know you just saved my life,\Nbut I'm actually looking for a church.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:23.63,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,A church?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:28.63,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The headquarters of the Leto religion, the cause of the riot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you go in, there won't be anything left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:45.36,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a passage that leads underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.36,0:14:48.70,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, there is, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:55.49,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.20,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,A poisoned reservoir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.50,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,It was already like that when we found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:09.51,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,So an ordinary human won't be able to get past this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.05,0:15:10.76,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:11.51,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:12.72,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you step in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:23.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:28.32,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,You mean... alchemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:33.62,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go a bit further,\Nso could you wait for me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:50.88,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:54.39,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,This place is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:58.51,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him, making something so large.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.65,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.83,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh, that wasn't even enough to slow you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:28.38,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:32.01,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I trap you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.68,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Uh oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.56,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:07.00,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Aren't you going to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:08.75,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:13.26,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,You... You're Van Hohenheim, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:17.76,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this is as far as you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:23.27,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if you go any further?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:27.98,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Going past this line will result in your death, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.02,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of like that flask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:38.41,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,So, my conclusion is you can only move within this tunnel and in the center portion of Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.70,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.08,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:50.25,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Why don't you say something, Mr. Can't-Leave-His-Home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.17,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:59.64,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as wrath within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.89,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Not just wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:07.69,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I left all of my unnecessary emotions within Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:10.52,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.73,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:15.28,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so that stands for "avarice".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:21.28,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,They say man is embodied by seven deadly sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:23.16,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Lust.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.04,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:26.91,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Sloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.41,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:30.67,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.63,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:36.67,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,And... Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:43.39,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,So the emotion he let go of first was you. "Pride".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:49.44,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Funny how he detached you to look exactly as he did when he was in the flask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:57.36,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,So that appearance itself is the true nature of that arrogant, self-adulating father of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:01.49,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask that you visit my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:04.28,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no need to rush things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:06.54,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry; I'd visit him even if I weren't invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:10.00,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him this:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.29,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,"Slave Number 23 will be coming to see you soon."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:19.42,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,"Throw yourself back in your chair in Central while you wait for him."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.30,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.97,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:28.47,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Van Hohenheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:41.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:46.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Find anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.74,0:19:48.12,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:52.00,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,People shouldn't go near this place. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.54,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell everyone not to go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.72,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.85,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:14.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your shift is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:18.36,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! The blizzard was killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:22.78,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go have a cup of bad coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:35.29,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:39.21,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,The Drakman army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:45.43,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,Drakma to the north has declared open hostilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.43,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,All men, battle positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:48.39,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.06,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,Drakma to the north has declared open hostilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.18,Default,Ann,0000,0000,0000,,All men, battle positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:12.16,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're lucky the Northern Wall of Briggs isn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:14.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Sir Kimblee?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:20.71,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, there are many men loyal to me in the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:26.26,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Once the battle begins, they'll betray the others, causing the fort to be thrown into confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:32.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,At last, I shall take Briggs by storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The fort that has stood in the way of Drakma for eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:38.90,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for the declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:42.82,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Let's launch some fireworks, shall we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.70,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,All cannons at the ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:56.58,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:35.30,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right. My name is Zampano.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:36.93,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,One of Kimblee's men.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:41.19,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor Marcoh is currently hiding in the slums of Asbec.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:44.73,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate you telling us, Zampano.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:46.82,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll guarantee your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.24,0:23:52.61,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Marcoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:56.49,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Things are getting interesting!
